00:12:48.366 --> 00:12:49.916 A:middle
to be Full Screen-capable.

00:12:50.286 --> 00:12:52.426 A:middle
But it could still
be added as a tile

00:12:52.666 --> 00:12:54.466 A:middle
to another Full Screen-capable
window.

00:12:55.016 --> 00:12:57.296 A:middle
