00:13:32.096 --> 00:13:35.216 A:middle
In addition, you might have a
window, you take it Full Screen,

00:13:35.216 --> 00:13:36.836 A:middle
and you want it to
always be alone.

00:13:37.356 --> 00:13:39.886 A:middle
You can set Full Screen
